The black should be on
the left, and the white

00:42:31.580 --> 00:42:32.538
should be on the right.

00:42:32.538 --> 00:42:34.720
You can see how small that is.

00:42:34.720 --> 00:42:37.220
I'm very glad somebody had that
amount of care and attention

00:42:37.220 --> 00:42:39.460
to get them the right
way round and to comment

00:42:39.460 --> 00:42:42.360
that I'd missed that
particular detail.

00:42:42.360 --> 00:42:45.630
And so that's the
final map of Braavos.

00:42:45.630 --> 00:42:47.590
So that's the end of the talk.

00:42:47.590 --> 00:42:49.757
Now we've got like eight
minutes left for questions.

